{"tid":1482001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說「停止捉鬼」試著說「任何時候保持冷靜理智」","createTime":"2019-08-18T02:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T06:53:15.000Z","uid":192517,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17533f2335583cca73fb20c435e1ba8224066f78","tid":1482001,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"預咗食負皮，有風向話停止捉鬼<br />\n因為五年前就係輸係呢度<br />\n<br />\n係，呢啲係事實，主要係和理非唔信任前線，自己內耗。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過今次唔撚同呀！</span></span>點解過左兩個月都唔理解我哋已經一條心，香港人唔會有鬼，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啲鬼係真係支那派落嚟而冇任何道德底線！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明都講左好多次係有可能會嚟殺狗屈示威者毁滅運動，討論又冇，預先煲大又冇，點預防又冇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通好明顯又唔捉咩，問題係捉嗰一刻我哋會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">情緒高脹</span></span>，會被<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煽動</span></span>，所以要無時無刻保持<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冷靜</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我講下我諗到有咩劇本：<br />\n會有鬼自己<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做過激行為/煽動/自己自爆</span></span>，引發情緒失控場境混亂，然後有狗就突然死咗啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以係超遠距離殺，又可以係事先喺狗糧落毒，計定時間先引發混亂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係！咁係會冇影到示威者殺狗，但觀感上真係會似示威者殺！<br />\n真係要認真討論點拆！我暫時諗到係就算捉到鬼點都要冷靜，我哋事先諗下要點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdc9a7c26cda521ed15897e358716fc712837d5","tid":1482001,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb03c4989459bbac98451b43ef252670effd919","tid":1482001,"uid":216253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:53:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82a1ec4c687738cc0a30d547a146db5610c7c7c5","tid":1482001,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db58d2aa86e1b78c23c622d9f584a3cfedadf1e8","tid":1482001,"uid":184597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n個問題既根結 唔係有冇鬼<br />\n而係大家都唔好犯錯呀"},{"pid":"848704333f0c35cb8927a70ccbe3254d9afe586f","tid":1482001,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"樓主哥哥，有人扮示威者都開通天咯，Mon Post 嘅警察又知咯，記者一個二個又知道。噉仲有咩特別要做呢？次次都會有人搞事啦，次次都預咗警察會開槍殺人啦，今次有咩唔同呀？<br />\n🥨☕"},{"pid":"d1a4c8f3b347964ead540dcd91437ecb81a96cd4","tid":1482001,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"848704333f0c35cb8927a70ccbe3254d9afe586f","tid":1482001,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"樓主哥哥，有人扮示威者都開通天咯，Mon Post 嘅警察又知咯，記者一個二個又知道。噉仲有咩特別要做呢？次次都會有人搞事啦，次次都預咗警察會開槍殺人啦，今次有咩唔同呀？<br />\n🥨☕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"唔同咪係總會有一次有人真係會死囉，唔通咁都叫「有咩唔同」<img src=\"/assets/faces/no